Name: Disease.sh API
Description: A third Party API for reliable global disease information.

Endpoints.Name: Global COVID-19 Totals
Endpoints.Description: Get global COVID-19 totals for today, yesterday and two days ago

Parameters.Name: yesterday
Parameters.Description: Queries data reported a day ago

Parameters.Name: twoDaysAgo
Parameters.Description: Queries data reported two days ago

Parameters.Name: allowNull
Parameters.Description: By default, if a value is missing, it is returned as 0. This allows nulls to be returned

TestCases.Name: Test Get global COVID-19 totals for today, yesterday and two days ago
TestCases.Description: Get global COVID-19 totals for today, yesterday and two days ago

Endpoints.Name: COVID-19 Totals for a Country
Endpoints.Description: Get COVID-19 totals for a specific country

Parameters.Name: country
Parameters.Description: A country name, iso2, iso3, or country ID code

Parameters.Name: yesterday
Parameters.Description: Queries data reported a day ago

Parameters.Name: twoDaysAgo
Parameters.Description: Queries data reported two days ago

Parameters.Name: strict
Parameters.Description: Setting to false gives you the ability to fuzzy search countries (i.e. Oman vs. rOMANia)

Parameters.Name: allowNull
Parameters.Description: By default, if a value is missing, it is returned as 0. This allows nulls to be returned

TestCases.Name: Test COVID-19 Totals for a Country
TestCases.Description: Get COVID-19 totals for a specific country

Endpoints.Name: COVID-19 Totals for a Set of Countries
Endpoints.Description: Get COVID-19 totals for a specific set of countries

Parameters.Name: countries
Parameters.Description: Multiple country names, iso2, iso3, or country IDs separated by commas

Parameters.Name: yesterday
Parameters.Description: Queries data reported a day ago

Parameters.Name: twoDaysAgo
Parameters.Description: Queries data reported two days ago

Parameters.Name: allowNull
Parameters.Description: By default, if a value is missing, it is returned as 0. This allows nulls to be returned

TestCases.Name: Test COVID-19 Totals for a Set of Countries
TestCases.Description: Get COVID-19 totals for a specific set of countries

EndpointGroups.Name: COVID-19: Worldometers
EndpointGroups.Description: (COVID-19 data sourced from Worldometers, updated every 10 minutes)
